<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="de">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Quiz-Ergebnis · Spanisch</title>
<meta name="quiz-meta" content="Spanisch Klasse 6–7 · Fehlerauswertung 26.03.2026">
<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nunito:wght@400;700;800;900&family=Caveat:wght@600;700&display=swap');

- { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

body {
font-family: ‘Nunito’, sans-serif;
background: #f0f4ff;
min-height: 100vh;
display: flex;
flex-direction: column;
align-items: center;
padding: 40px 20px 60px;
}

.title-block {
text-align: center;
margin-bottom: 10px;
}
.title-block h1 {
font-size: clamp(22px, 4vw, 36px);
font-weight: 900;
color: #2d5a9e;
}
.title-block .sub {
font-family: ‘Caveat’, cursive;
font-size: 22px;
color: #e17055;
margin-top: 4px;
}
.title-block .date {
font-size: 13px;
color: #8a9bb5;
font-weight: 700;
margin-top: 6px;
letter-spacing: 1px;
text-transform: uppercase;
}

.chart-card {
background: white;
border-radius: 20px;
padding: 32px 36px;
width: 100%;
max-width: 640px;
box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(45,90,158,0.10);
margin-top: 28px;
}

.chart-card h2 {
font-size: 16px;
font-weight: 800;
color: #2d5a9e;
margin-bottom: 28px;
text-align: center;
letter-spacing: 0.5px;
}

.cat { margin-bottom: 20px; }

.cat-top {
display: flex;
justify-content: space-between;
align-items: center;
margin-bottom: 7px;
}

.cat-name {
font-size: 14px;
font-weight: 800;
color: #2d3436;
display: flex;
align-items: center;
gap: 7px;
}

.cat-sub {
font-size: 11px;
font-weight: 600;
color: #8a9bb5;
margin-top: -4px;
margin-bottom: 7px;
padding-left: 24px;
}

.pct-badge {
font-size: 13px;
font-weight: 900;
padding: 3px 11px;
border-radius: 20px;
}

.track {
height: 13px;
background: #eef2fb;
border-radius: 10px;
overflow: hidden;
}
.fill {
height: 100%;
border-radius: 10px;
animation: grow 1.2s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1) forwards;
transform-origin: left;
}
@keyframes grow {
from { width: 0 }
}

/* severity */
.red  .fill { background: linear-gradient(90deg,#d63031,#e17055); }
.red  .pct-badge { background: #fdecea; color: #d63031; }
.ora  .fill { background: linear-gradient(90deg,#e17055,#fdcb6e); }
.ora  .pct-badge { background: #fdf0ec; color: #c0530a; }
.yel  .fill { background: linear-gradient(90deg,#fdcb6e,#ffeaa7); }
.yel  .pct-badge { background: #fef9ec; color: #9a6c00; }
.grn  .fill { background: linear-gradient(90deg,#00b894,#55efc4); }
.grn  .pct-badge { background: #e8f8f5; color: #007a63; }

.legend {
display: flex;
flex-wrap: wrap;
gap: 10px 18px;
justify-content: center;
margin-top: 28px;
font-size: 12px;
font-weight: 700;
color: #636e72;
}
.leg-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; }
.leg-dot {
width: 11px; height: 11px;
border-radius: 50%;
flex-shrink: 0;
}

.footer {
margin-top: 28px;
font-family: ‘Caveat’, cursive;
font-size: 20px;
color: #2d5a9e;
text-align: center;
opacity: 0.75;
}
</style>

</head>
<body>

<div class="title-block">
  <h1>🇪🇸 So hat die Klasse abgeschnitten</h1>
  <div class="sub">¡Muy bien, clase!</div>
  <div class="date">Quiz · 26. März 2026 · 21 Schülerinnen & Schüler · Ø 82 %</div>
</div>

<div class="chart-card">
  <h2>Wo lagen die meisten Fehler?</h2>

  <div class="cat red">
    <div class="cat-top">
      <div class="cat-name">🔴 Imperativ <em>tú</em></div>
      <div class="pct-badge">76 %</div>
    </div>
    <div class="cat-sub">¡Escucha! · ¡Habla! · ¡Come! – die tú-Form des Imperativs</div>
    <div class="track"><div class="fill" style="width:76%"></div></div>
  </div>

  <div class="cat ora">
    <div class="cat-top">
      <div class="cat-name">🟠 Adjektivkongruenz</div>
      <div class="pct-badge">48 %</div>
    </div>
    <div class="cat-sub">rubio/rubia, largo/larga – Angleichung an Genus & Stellung</div>
    <div class="track"><div class="fill" style="width:48%"></div></div>
  </div>

  <div class="cat ora">
    <div class="cat-top">
      <div class="cat-name">🟠 Unregelmäßige Verben</div>
      <div class="pct-badge">43 %</div>
    </div>
    <div class="cat-sub">ir → vas / vais · poder → puedes / podéis</div>
    <div class="track"><div class="fill" style="width:43%"></div></div>
  </div>

  <div class="cat ora">
    <div class="cat-top">
      <div class="cat-name">🟠 Objektpronomen</div>
      <div class="pct-badge">38 %</div>
    </div>
    <div class="cat-sub">lo / la / los / las – Position vor dem Verb</div>
    <div class="track"><div class="fill" style="width:38%"></div></div>
  </div>

  <div class="cat ora">
    <div class="cat-top">
      <div class="cat-name">🟠 Wortschatz</div>
      <div class="pct-badge">38 %</div>
    </div>
    <div class="cat-sub">comida principal – Alltagsvokabular</div>
    <div class="track"><div class="fill" style="width:38%"></div></div>
  </div>

  <div class="cat yel">
    <div class="cat-top">
      <div class="cat-name">🟡 Estar + Gerundio</div>
      <div class="pct-badge">29 %</div>
    </div>
    <div class="cat-sub">están jugando – Verlaufsform</div>
    <div class="track"><div class="fill" style="width:29%"></div></div>
  </div>

  <div class="cat yel">
    <div class="cat-top">
      <div class="cat-name">🟡 Pretérito indefinido</div>
      <div class="pct-badge">29 %</div>
    </div>
    <div class="cat-sub">comí – yo-Form regelmäßiger Verben</div>
    <div class="track"><div class="fill" style="width:29%"></div></div>
  </div>

  <div class="cat yel">
    <div class="cat-top">
      <div class="cat-name">🟡 Futuro: ir a + infinitivo</div>
      <div class="pct-badge">29 %</div>
    </div>
    <div class="cat-sub">vamos a ir al cine</div>
    <div class="track"><div class="fill" style="width:29%"></div></div>
  </div>

  <div class="cat grn">
    <div class="cat-top">
      <div class="cat-name">🟢 Ser vs. Estar</div>
      <div class="pct-badge">24 %</div>
    </div>
    <div class="cat-sub">estar enfermo – Zustände mit estar</div>
    <div class="track"><div class="fill" style="width:24%"></div></div>
  </div>

  <div class="cat grn">
    <div class="cat-top">
      <div class="cat-name">🟢 Presente · Artikel · Komparativ</div>
      <div class="pct-badge">&lt; 20 %</div>
    </div>
    <div class="cat-sub">Das sitzt schon sehr gut! ✓</div>
    <div class="track"><div class="fill" style="width:16%"></div></div>
  </div>

  <div class="legend">
    <div class="leg-item"><div class="leg-dot" style="background:#d63031"></div> über 70 % – dringend üben</div>
    <div class="leg-item"><div class="leg-dot" style="background:#e17055"></div> 40–69 % – noch unsicher</div>
    <div class="leg-item"><div class="leg-dot" style="background:#fdcb6e"></div> 20–39 % – fast da</div>
    <div class="leg-item"><div class="leg-dot" style="background:#00b894"></div> unter 20 % – gut bekannt</div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="footer">¡Sigue así, clase! 💪</div>

<div style="margin-top:28px;text-align:center">
  <a href="../index.html" style="font-family:'Nunito',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:800;color:#8a9bb5;text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:1px;">← Zurück zur Übersicht</a>
</div>

</body>
</html>